{
  "captions": [
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- If you let yourself,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:10.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>you can really imagine what the decisions</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:12.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>you made could mean.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:15.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>The path you've lit forward.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:18.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I think that in knowing in the early days,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:21.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>they will rely on us for everything,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:25.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>it can drive a fear that\ncan drive you to want</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:30.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to protect them from whatever you can.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:34.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But when I cast my mind</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:41.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>into the future of this\nlife I have created,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:42.760"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>all I hope is that it is\na life lived joyously,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:47.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>freely, fulfilled.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:52.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I think if I had a wish for them,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:58.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>it would be that it\nwould have the security</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:02.360"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to be who they wanted to be,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:06.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to find a purpose that brings\nthem more happiness than pain.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:09.559"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Because, well,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:15.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>because isn't that the best\nwe can hope for in life?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:18.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And I can't see why that's\nnot achievable for most,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:23.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>if not all children.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:26.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And I suspect that it's less</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:31.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>about choosing the children\nthat come into the world</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:35.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>than choosing a better\nworld for these children</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:39.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to come into.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:41.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For our problem is and always has been</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:44.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>how we ensure that\nbetter world comes about.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:48.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and that problem must be </b>\n<b>answered beyond these walls..</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:51.840"
    }
  ]
}